  "text": "The homogenized sample (1 mL) was directly poured from the vial into the sample cup and covered with the reflector. The transparent bottom of the sample cup was visually checked to ensure there were no air bubbles. The sample cup was positioned on the instrument and scanned for 60 s. Reference scans were automatically performed to check calibration every 30 min. Daily quality controls were performed as described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
